{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, by Assumption 4.4(iv), we have for the fifth term on the right-hand side of inequality (6.9)",
    "Next, for the sixth term on the right-hand side of inequality (6.9), we obtain using Burkholder-Davis-Gundy inequality",
    ", for all ε > 0.",
    "The second term on the right-hand side of this inequality can be estimated as in (6.10).",
    "Finally, for the last term in inequality (6.9), we obtain again using Burkholder-Davis-Gundy inequality"
  ]
}